data.description: Contemporary with historic charm - this 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath, 2-story home on Wausau's East Side offers tasteful updates - modern colors & accents, high-end finishes and immense attention-to-detail. All new vinyl plank flooring throughout with marble-tile throughout the eating areas. White-washed fireplace with a large study / sunroom. Stunning kitchen with Featherstone cabinetry, new sink & faucet, counters and appliances! Main level half bath and storage closet. Semi-open staircase with exposed railing w/ new flooring. Upper level with 3 bedrooms, all freshly designed / painted with tiled hallway flooring. Modernized full upper bath with shiplap accent, new light fixtures and vanity. Partially finished lower level with rec room & pellet stove - great storage or future finished area. Future main level dog wash area - already tiled / stubbed for plumbing. 2-car detached garage, fenced back yard, and landscaping around the entire home. Schedule your showing today!
